ABOUT NATIONSTAR   We Are Nationstar











 Customer-centric. Experienced. Growing.   With a relentless focus on providing quality solutions to our customers, Nationstar has become one of the largest and fastest growing mortgage servicers in the United States with a servicing portfolio of approximately $470 billion and more than 3 million customers.  
Our integrated approach, the strength and diversity of our services operations, and our strategies for growing all segments of our business, position us to be a long term leader in our industry. 














 A Culture of Caring   Because we are focused on keeping people in their homes, it’s natural for us to want to do all we can to help those who are truly struggling. That’s why we continue to develop programs and volunteering opportunities to help others, while making our team even stronger. This includes the creation of our Community Outreach Team, our Random Acts of Kindness project and our continuing participation with Habitat for Humanity.  Learn more 











 Deep in the Heart   Headquartered in North Texas, with offices located around the country, we’re blessed with an incredible culture that promotes innovation, enthusiasm and passion. We support our team with special events like Artists in Residence that help our employees relax, build relationships and inspire new ideas. 











 Strength in Business   Nationstar offers servicing, origination, and transaction-based real estate services to all of our customers, including: homeowners, home buyers, home sellers, investors, and other real estate market participants. Learn more   








