Services Our diversity of services and performance set us apart. Nationstar offers clients one of the broadest menus of services in the residential mortgage services industry, helping to optimize asset performance while improving the borrower's experience. We combine our high-touch mortgage servicing with a fully integrated loan originations platform, supported by our Xome® business which provides services spanning the real estate and mortgage markets, creating customers for life. Nationstar offers clients a diversified array of residential mortgage services:


 Servicing  We are one of the largest independent loan servicers in the United States with a demonstrated track record of excellent asset performance. Our servicing portfolio consists of purchased mortgage servicing assets, subservicing, and servicing via loan origination. Read More   




 Originations  We operate an integrated loan origination platform. We currently originate prime agency and government conforming residential mortgage loans. We are licensed to originate residential mortgage loans in 49 states and D.C. Read More   




 Xome  Xome offers an array of services, including real estate exchange, title, close, escrow, valuation, and asset management services.  Read More     






