Corporate Profile







Webcast 

Q1 2017 Earnings Conference Call
Presentation

May 4, 2017 | 9:00 AM ET

Nationstar Mortgage (NYSE:NSM) Nationstar earns fees through 
the delivery of quality servicing, origination and transaction based services principally 
related to single-family residences throughout the United States. Nationstar is 
one of the largest servicers in the United States, with a residential mortgage servicing 
portfolio of approximately $470 billion in unpaid principal balance, and nearly 3 million customers as of March 31, 2017. Nationstar provides services and solutions to 
homeowners, home buyers, home sellers, investors and other real estate market participants.




