Nationstar Mortgage Holdings Inc




				 24 July, 2017,  11:30 | Author: Terri Saunders			













Geron Corporation (NASDAQ:GERN) has risen 13.81% since July 21, 2016 and is uptrending. It has outperformed by 12.98% the S&P500.The move comes after 5 months negative chart setup for the $13.10 billion company. NSM's SI was 4.82 million shares in July as released by FINRA.Since January 23, 2017, it had 0 insider purchases, and 6 sales for $4.04 million activity. Tudor Investment Corp Et Al purchased a new stake in Nationstar Mortgage Holdings during the fourth quarter valued at approximately $279,000. The SI to Nationstar Mortgage Holdings Incorporated's float is 17.3%. Nationstar Mortgage Holdings has a 1-year low of $11.76 and a 1-year high of $19.83. It has outperformed by 29.98% the S&P500. Finally, Highbridge Capital Management LLC bought a new position in shares of Nationstar Mortgage Holdings during the fourth quarter worth about $763,000. On average, analysts expect that Nationstar Mortgage Holdings will post $1.28 earnings per share for the current year. Zacks Investment Research upgraded Nationstar Mortgage Holdings from a "sell" rating to a "buy" rating and set a $20.00 price target on the stock in a report on Thursday. On Friday, February 26 the stock rating was maintained by FBR Capital with "Mkt Perform". RBC Capital Markets maintained the stock with "Buy" rating in Wednesday, July 19 report. As per Wednesday, November 4, the company rating was maintained by Oppenheimer. The stock has "Outperform" rating by Credit Suisse on Monday, March 7. The stock of Nationstar Mortgage Holdings Inc (NYSE:NSM) earned "Neutral" rating by Piper Jaffray on Friday, September 9.Nationstar Mortgage Holdings (NYSE:NSM) last posted its quarterly earnings results on Thursday, May 4th.Investors sentiment increased to 1.03 in Q4 2016. Its up 0.49, from 0.62 in 2016Q3. The ratio increased, as 59 active investment managers started new and increased holdings, while 53 sold and decreased their equity positions in Nationstar Mortgage Holdings Inc. 26 funds opened positions while 33 raised stakes. Cantab Cap Ptnrs Limited Liability Partnership holds 0% or 35,429 shares in its portfolio. Millennium Mgmt Ltd Llc holds 0% or 11,986 shares. (NYSE NSM) traded up 0.50% on Friday, reaching $18.14. Alliancebernstein Lp owns 0% invested in Geron Corporation (NASDAQ:GERN) for 196,211 shares. 22,607 were accumulated by State Board Of Administration Of Florida Retirement Sys. Pacad Investment Ltd. raised its stake in Nationstar Mortgage Holdings by 2.3% in the fourth quarter. The New York-based Adirondack Research & Management Inc. has invested 2.12% in the stock.
