Nationstar Mortgage Holdings Inc. Reports Unaudited Consolidated Earnings Results for the First Quarter Ended March 31, 2017
May 4 17
Nationstar Mortgage Holdings Inc. reported unaudited consolidated earnings results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2017. For the quarter, the company reported total revenues of USD 427 million, income before income tax expense of USD 317 million, net income of USD 198 million, net income attributable to the company of USD 198 million or diluted earnings per share of USD 2.01 per share. Adjusted earnings was USD 35 million or USD 0.36 per share. Adjusted pretax income was USD 47 million.


