Car Makes & Models












Q:
What is the official plural of Prius?


A:
The official plural of Prius when referring to the car is Prii. In Latin, the plural of the word pruis is priora.


See Full Answer

Filed Under:


Car Makes & Models












Q:
How Many People Can You Fit in a Limousine?


A:
The number of people that fit in a limousine varies according to the size, type and model of the limousine. On average, the number of people that fit in a limousine ranges from six in smaller limousines to 15 or more in stretch limousines.


See Full Answer

